The paper deals with constraint satisfaction problems (CSPs) and introduces a new type of operation called generalized majority-minority (GMM) operations. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), logic in computer science (cs.LO), or discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
